es de ce vingt-et-unième siècle en quête de sens.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 4aHumanities & Social Sciences. 4aMedicine. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aDworczak, Fabien, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Contemporary eBook-Package 2016-2020z978311075640140uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-2466-340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759824663423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9782759824663.jpg  a978-3-11-075640-1  EDP Sciences Contemporary eBook-Package 2016-2020c2016d2020  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK